      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776001000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. factor_id / factor_version / factor_direction 是否冻结\n2. factor_role / factor_structure / portfolio_expression / neutralization 是否与上游一致\n3. factor_panel 是否唯一表示同一时点不同资产的因子值\n4. raw fields / derived fields / final score 字段是否写清\n5. eligibility / coverage / missing 传递规则是否冻结\n6. 多因子是否仍是确定性公式，而不是 learned weights",
      "rawText": "1. factor_id / factor_version / factor_direction 是否冻结\n2. factor_role / factor_structure / portfolio_expression / neutralization 是否与上游一致\n3. factor_panel 是否唯一表示同一时点不同资产的因子值\n4. raw fields / derived fields / final score 字段是否写清\n5. eligibility / coverage / missing 传递规则是否冻结\n6. 多因子是否仍是确定性公式，而不是 learned weights",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. factor_id / factor_version / factor_direction 是否冻结\n2. factor_role / factor_structure / portfolio_expression / neutralization 是否与上游一致\n3. factor_panel 是否唯一表示同一时点不同资产的因子值\n4. raw fields / derived fields / final score 字段是否写清\n5. eligibility / coverage / missing 传递规则是否冻结\n6. 多因子是否仍是确定性公式，而不是 learned weights",
      "autoResize": true,
