      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. 五组都确认：factor_identity / factor_role / factor_structure / neutralization / delivery\n2. factor_role 三选一、factor_structure 二选一都明确\n3. portfolio_expression 与 neutralization_policy 明确冻结\n4. group_neutral 场景下必须有 taxonomy 引用\n5. 真实生成 factor_panel / manifest / coverage / contract / dictionaries",
      "rawText": "1. 五组都确认：factor_identity / factor_role / factor_structure / neutralization / delivery\n2. factor_role 三选一、factor_structure 二选一都明确\n3. portfolio_expression 与 neutralization_policy 明确冻结\n4. group_neutral 场景下必须有 taxonomy 引用\n5. 真实生成 factor_panel / manifest / coverage / contract / dictionaries",
