      "updated": 1776001000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "真实交付：\n- factor_panel.parquet\n- factor_manifest.yaml\n- factor_coverage.parquet\n- factor_contract.md\n- factor_field_dictionary.md\n- signal_gate_decision.md\n- artifact_catalog.md / field_dictionary.md\n\n实现提醒：\n- 前置约束：只有在 02_csf_data_ready review closure 完成后才能进入\n- 不得静默修改 panel 主键、membership、eligibility 或时间边界\n- Review 侧常写 factor_coverage_report.parquet，落地实现时要统一正式文件名并写映射\n- 通过 review closure 后，才进入 05 CSF Train Freeze",
      "rawText": "真实交付：\n- factor_panel.parquet\n- factor_manifest.yaml\n- factor_coverage.parquet\n- factor_contract.md\n- factor_field_dictionary.md\n- signal_gate_decision.md\n- artifact_catalog.md / field_dictionary.md\n\n实现提醒：\n- 前置约束：只有在 02_csf_data_ready review closure 完成后才能进入\n- 不得静默修改 panel 主键、membership、eligibility 或时间边界\n- Review 侧常写 factor_coverage_report.parquet，落地实现时要统一正式文件名并写映射\n- 通过 review closure 后，才进入 05 CSF Train Freeze",
      "fontSize": 12,
